snippet.title: Sensible World of Soccer 96/97 Longplay - Amiga - Season 1
snippet.description:
Longplay of Sensible World of Soccer, 96/97 edition on the Amiga.

Obviously not a game with a traditional start and end, so this is part 1 of my challenge I used to do back in the day. Take Barnet from the English 3rd division and win the Premier League.

Part 1 of possible a lot of videos.

Some edits for loading and breaks, but otherwise as it happened (as you can see from the number of injuries).

Season 2 now available here - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hCO7Mb5YP4Q
